<p>Hi <%= @user.first_name || @user.email_address %>,</p>

<p>This is a friendly reminder that the book "<strong><%= @book.title %></strong>" is due soon.</p>

<% if @borrow.due_at.present? %>
  <p><strong>Due date:</strong> <%= @borrow.due_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %></p>
<% end %>

<p>You can view your borrowed books in BookSwap to return it when you're ready.</p>

